  "body": "I'm doing new installation of remixd (global)\r\n```\r\nsudo npm install -g @remix-project/remixd --force\r\n```\r\nAnd command to start every time returns me an error\r\n```\r\nremixd -s /Users/me/test --remix-ide https://remix.ethereum.org\r\n```\r\n```\r\nzsh: no such file or directory: remixd -s /Users/me/test/ --remix-ide https://remix.ethereum.org\r\n```\r\nBut this directory is 100% exists. I tried different versions of remixd its haven't helped\r\nMy OS is Mac OS Big Sur 11.2.3",
