    "body": "I think this will help.\r\n\r\nAdd this command to `~/.bash_profile`\r\n\r\n```\r\nexport PATH=\"$HOME/.npm-global/bin:$PATH\"\r\n```\r\nAnd then, add this to `~/.zshrc`\r\n\r\n```\r\nsource $HOME/.bash_profile\r\n```\r\n\r\nIf you do this and restart the terminal, the 'remixd' command will work fine.\r\n\r\nI'm leaving my OS in case you're curious\r\nmy OS is mac OS Monterey 12.3.1",
